title: 'No option for replacement when size is misfit'
body: 'The blazer turned out to be a bit small around the chest and short sleeve so I simply wanted a bigger size. But when I tried to replace there is only refund option and dispatch to be done from my side bearing full cost. Never buy from this seller. Even wonder why Amazon allows such a process.'
